description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Imaging Lead&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;North West London – Brentford TW8&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Riverside Clinic&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Salary: £45000-£51000 (dependent on experience)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Healthshare is a successful provider of clinical and diagnostic services to the NHS and private sectors across various locations throughout the country.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Riverside Clinic is a new Day Surgery Unit, which comprises of 8 beds, 1 theatre, 4 Recovery Bays.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a dynamic, caring and enthusiastic leader to provide excellent clinical and operational leadership of the imaging department at The Riverside Clinic. We currently have a Simens 3T MRI scanner, DR Gem X-Ray room, image intensifier and soon to be installed Fuji DXA machine.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a lead radiographer who has significant experience in MRI and plain film and is willing to learning DXA.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are looking for new opportunities and challenges in a management role then this post could be for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post-holder should possess a BSc/DCR in Radiography, or equivalent and be a HCPC state-registered Radiographer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With overall responsibility for imaging services at The Riverside clinic, the post-holder will be responsible for the provision of a high quality, responsive, patient-focused service, providing clinical leadership with a high degree of professionalism and ensuring effective utilisation and control of all resources.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post-holder will work closely with the Executive Director and liaise with operational managers Attendance at local, regional and national meetings will be required to ensure service provision that reflects current guidance in line with recommendations for best practice and to enhance the profile of the clinic.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please see Job Description for full details and personal specification.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Like the sound of this role? Don’t miss out – apply now!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
